{"tid":1862523,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香草餅乾咖啡杯","createTime":"2020-02-04T16:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T18:56:38.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"befb184bf847dbaccbeaac7884cc8e940e563430","tid":1862523,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/fotojet-2019-12-17t182634-104-1576578407.jpg?crop=1.00xw:1.00xh;0,0&amp;resize=768:* \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Ffotojet-2019-12-17t182634-104-1576578407.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1.00xw%3A1.00xh%3B0%2C0%26resize%3D768%3A%2A%20&h=2e726d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年環保議題被各界重視，用紙吸管取代塑膠、自備餐具成為一種生活默契，然而每年大量搭機出國旅行的乘客必須使用一次性餐具，不可避免的在飛機旅途中產生垃圾。現在紐西蘭航空用超棒的方式響應環保，與紐西蘭當地企業Twiice合作開發「可食用咖啡杯」，用香草餅乾體製作的杯子超有創意，喝完咖啡就可以直接把餅乾吃掉！<br />\n<br />\n可食用「香草餅乾咖啡杯」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/flight-attendant-pouring-into-cup-aircups1219-1576574149.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:* \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fflight-attendant-pouring-into-cup-aircups1219-1576574149.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A%20&h=cb909af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAIR NEW ZEALAND<br />\n<br />\n這款餅乾可以裝咖啡，也真的可以吃！紐西蘭航空與當地企業Twiice合作的咖啡杯是用小麥粉、糖、雞蛋與香草製作而成，香草餅乾的杯體酥脆，與機上提供的黑咖啡更是美味的絕配組合～（蛋奶素可食用）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/air-new-zealand-edible-coffee-cup-from-twiice-3-916x516-1576574148.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:* \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fair-new-zealand-edible-coffee-cup-from-twiice-3-916x516-1576574148.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A%20&h=98d757d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAIR NEW ZEALAND<br />\n<br />\n為了製作出健康可食用同時不會軟爛的餅乾咖啡杯，生產商Twiice費盡心思運用多種不同原料的樣品進行試用，紐西蘭航空資深顧客體驗經理Niki Chave表示：「公司同仁對產品測試方面是很嚴格的，同事們將香草餅乾杯帶回家實際試用了好一陣子，並互相分享照片，藉此改進。」<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭航空對這項創意產品充滿信心，相信已經通過最終實測上線的「香草餅乾咖啡杯」不會讓大家失望的！<br />\n<br />\n還可以裝冰淇淋！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/air-new-zealand-edible-coffee-cup-from-twiice-3-1-916x516-1576574147.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:* \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fair-new-zealand-edible-coffee-cup-from-twiice-3-1-916x516-1576574147.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A%20&h=60cae0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAIR NEW ZEALAND<br />\n<br />\n除了盛裝咖啡給乘客品嚐，香草餅乾咖啡杯也可以裝上冰淇淋，搖身一變成為甜品杯，就像是一般的冰淇淋甜筒，香滑綿密的冰淇淋搭上酥脆餅乾的口感一吃就上癮～<br />\n<br />\n減少一次性垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/airnz-74873341-1419248901562958-3180590220404799900-n-1576577309.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:* \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fairnz-74873341-1419248901562958-3180590220404799900-n-1576577309.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A%20&h=86eed939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAIR NEW ZEALAND<br />\n<br />\n香草餅乾咖啡杯不只造型吸睛，在環保方面也有很大的幫助，這項紐西蘭航空和Twiice的合作計畫還在試推行期間，目前可食用咖啡杯計畫僅在「紐西蘭&mdash;澳洲」航線以及貴賓室啟用。<br />\n<br />\nNiki Chave也表示：「其餘航線目前使用的咖啡杯也是可分解的有機材質，但我們的最終目標是不再製造任何咖啡杯垃圾。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/airnz-72293123-2355188261476439-4103545359221523100-n-1576577255.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:* \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fairnz-72293123-2355188261476439-4103545359221523100-n-1576577255.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A%20&h=c4a27af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平均每天早上會消耗600杯咖啡、平均一年在空中與地面上加起來超過「800萬杯咖啡」的紐西蘭航空未來如果全面更換的話，一年就能減少數量超驚人的一次性紙杯垃圾！<br />\n<br />\n他們也表示可食用咖啡杯是第一步，未來也會致力研發其他可以長期使用的環保創意器具，為環境盡一份心力！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elle.com/tw/life/travel/g30251445/air-newzealand-cup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com%2Ftw%2Flife%2Ftravel%2Fg30251445%2Fair-newzealand-cup%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3SKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=2e7942d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elle.com/tw/life/travel/g30251445/air-newzealand-cup/</a>"},{"pid":"ad39f07c3ba5bd6f0c3b6086b050496178372a6b","tid":1862523,"uid":13361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"飲完咖啡再食餅乾 跟住口乾點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b26509ccc3a91570af1082d0b657aab978603e2","tid":1862523,"uid":148673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"其他人隻手掂過塊餅<br />\n點質落口呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9d89d0c712c89a23069aac0f642aac9f6573d7","tid":1862523,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b26509ccc3a91570af1082d0b657aab978603e2","tid":1862523,"uid":148673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"其他人隻手掂過塊餅<br />\n點質落口呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:52:48.000Z","msg":"飛雞隻手個頭幫人打完飛機<br />\n呢頭比杯野你<br />\n食埋個杯同幫人含撚有咩分別"},{"pid":"1cdec846a897fc2a1dbe9f7acbe65f9a2e00b969","tid":1862523,"uid":149662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:56:38.000Z","msg":"雖然呢樣野都一定好多bug<br />\n但我欣賞佢唔係好似環保少女咁淨係得個講字<br />\n而係真係有alternatives 俾到出黎<br />\n香港個啲淨係識唔派飲筒<br />\n但又無度過人地點飲<br />\n呢啲先on9"}]}